---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Dossier — SWAMP PAY" description="The mission and personnel behind SWAMP PAY sovereign payment terminals.">
  <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] overflow-hidden border-b border-olive/20 bg-midnight pt-24 pb-24">
    <img
      src={`${(import.meta.env.BASE_URL).replace(/\/$/, '')}/base.jpg`}
      alt=""
      class="war-photo-bg-hero"
      style="object-position: center 40%;"
      loading="eager"
      aria-hidden="true"
    />
    <div class="war-photo-overlay-light" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="film-grain absolute inset-0 z-[2]" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="stamp-classified text-xs text-napalm">Declassified</span>
        <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-khaki/20" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-stencil text-5xl tracking-wide text-white sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
        The Mission<br />
        <span class="text-phosphor crt-glow">Behind SWAMP</span>.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-bone/90">
        We build payment infrastructure that treats surveillance as a design flaw,
        not a feature. This is the dossier.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-b border-olive/20 bg-bunker py-24" aria-label="Mission">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label-military">Mission Statement</p>
          <h2 class="font-stencil text-3xl text-white">
            Financial privacy is a<br />
            <span class="text-amber crt-glow-amber">fundamental right</span>.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-smoke">
            SWAMP PAY was founded on a simple principle: the act of buying a cup of
            coffee should not generate a permanent, searchable record of your location,
            preferences, and habits.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-smoke">
            We engineer payment systems that process transactions without collecting
            the data that makes surveillance capitalism possible. Not through policies
            that can change — through architecture that can't. Like fortifying a firebase.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded border border-olive/20 bg-midnight/60 p-6">
            <p class="font-stencil text-xs text-khaki">[PRINCIPLE 01]</p>
            <h3 class="mt-2 font-stencil text-lg text-white">OPSEC by Architecture</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-smoke">
              What's better than privacy policies — writing code that makes data collection
              technically impossible. Architecture over promises. Fortification over faith.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded border border-olive/20 bg-midnight/60 p-6">
            <p class="font-stencil text-xs text-khaki">[PRINCIPLE 02]</p>
            <h3 class="mt-2 font-stencil text-lg text-white">Offline First</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-smoke">
              Internet goes down, the terminal keeps running. No cloud dependency
              means no single point of failure — and no one listening on the wire.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded border border-olive/20 bg-midnight/60 p-6">
            <p class="font-stencil text-xs text-khaki">[PRINCIPLE 03]</p>
            <h3 class="mt-2 font-stencil text-lg text-white">Merchant Sovereignty</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-smoke">
              Your terminal. Your data. Your customers. We provide infrastructure —
              not control. No lock-in, no platform dependency, no permission required.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="bg-bunker py-24" id="contact" aria-label="Contact">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
      <p class="section-label-military mx-auto">Secure Channel — Comms</p>
      <h2 class="font-stencil text-3xl text-white">Establish Contact</h2>
      <!-- <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-lg text-lg text-smoke">
        Encrypted communications preferred. PGP key available on request.
      </p> -->

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded border border-olive/20 bg-midnight/60 p-6">
          <p class="font-stencil text-xs text-khaki">GENERAL</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-sm text-phosphor">hello@swamppay.io</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded border border-olive/20 bg-midnight/60 p-6">
          <p class="font-stencil text-xs text-khaki">SIGNALS CORPS</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-sm text-phosphor">dev@swamppay.io</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded border border-olive/20 bg-midnight/60 p-6">
          <p class="font-stencil text-xs text-khaki">OPSEC</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-sm text-phosphor">security@swamppay.io</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- <p class="mt-8 font-mono text-xs text-khaki/50">
        <span class="text-phosphor-dim">[PGP]</span> Fingerprint: 4A2B 8C9D EF01 2345 6789 ABCD EF01 2345 6789 ABCD
      </p> -->
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
